24
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,950
♪Defining eternity♪

25
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:41,180
This is good.

26
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,420
It's your favorite.

27
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:44,460
Yeah.

28
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:47,780
I'm full.

29
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:48,980
You've barely eaten.

30
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:51,340
♪A tear lightly kisses my palm♪

31
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:52,260
Are you on a diet?

32
