♪Written in the starry night♪

36
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:21,470
♪Destined to be the only one♪

37
00:03:24,110 --> 00:03:28,250
♪How to describe my love for you♪

38
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:34,500
♪Because of you, love begins to breathe♪

39
